OL,7,FA man stabbed his estranged wife 18
OL,8,Ftimes and killed her at the shop where
OL,9,Fshe worked in anger over not being
OL,10,Finvited to a family event, a court has
OL,11,Fheard.
OL,13,FNimalarajah Mathiyadaranam, 47, is
OL,14,Fsaid to have attacked his wife, Nilani
OL,15,FNimalarajah, 44, with such ferocity
OL,16,Fthat the tip of the knife was "broken
OL,17,Foff".
