OL,7,FHe had already been banned from
OL,8,Fcontacting the mum of three by a court
OL,9,Forder due to previous cases of
OL,10,F"violence and harassment".
OL,12,FMathiyadaranam, of Warrington Road in
OL,13,FWidnes, went on trial at Liverpool
OL,14,FCrown Court on Wednesday 14 January,
OL,15,Faccused of murder.
