OL,7,FOpening for the prosecution Annabel
OL,8,FDarlow KC told the court: "On Friday
OL,9,Fthe 20th of June of last year, this
OL,10,Fdefendant, armed with a large knife,
OL,11,Fwent to a convenience store in Bootle
OL,12,Fhere in Liverpool, where his estranged
OL,13,Fwife, Nilani Nimalarajah, was working.
OL,14,FHe entered the store and stabbed his
OL,15,Fwife to death.
OL,17,F"It was a merciless, sustained and
OL,18,Fextremely brutal attack. He stabbed
OL,19,FNilani at least 18 times, deliberately
OL,20,Ftargeting the areas of her chest and
OL,21,Fher head.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
