OL,4,Cover not being invited to a family
OL,5,Cevent
OL,7,F"Indeed, he stabbed her with such
OL,8,Fferocity that it caused the tip of the
OL,9,Fknife to be broken off.
OL,11,F"The prosecution's case is that the
OL,12,Fdefendant deliberately planned this
OL,13,Fmurder. Hours before he killed Nilani,
OL,14,Fhe went to a shop where he purchased a
OL,15,Fwhole block of knives and some duct
OL,16,Ftape.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
