OL,3,CMan stabbed wife 18 times in anger
OL,4,Cover not being invited to a family
OL,5,Cevent
OL,7,F"The trigger for Nilani's murder
OL,8,Fappears to have been this defendant's
OL,9,Fanger and his misplaced sense of pride
OL,10,Fthat he had not been involved or
OL,11,Finvited into a significant family
OL,12,Fevent.
OL,14,F"The defendant is of Sri Lankan
OL,15,Fheritage, and part of his cultural
OL,16,Fheritage involves the family holding a
OL,17,Fcelebration when a girl has her first
OL,18,Fmenstrual period.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
