OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F391A1768410891
OL,3,CMan stabbed wife 18 times in anger
OL,4,Cover not being invited to a family
OL,5,Cevent
OL,7,F"Nilani's second daughter had recently
OL,8,Fcelebrated this milestone in her young
OL,9,Flife, but the defendant had not been
OL,10,Finvited to the traditional
OL,11,Fcelebration. His reaction was one of
OL,12,Fthe most appalling and pre-meditated
OL,13,Fviolence."
OL,15,FMathiyadaranam appeared in the dock
OL,16,Fassisted by an interpreter, and denies
OL,17,Fmurder, with the trial expected to
OL,18,Flast around a week.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
